      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A medium-hard, pale yellow variety of copal resin obtained from trees of the genus Copaifera native to Sierra Leone, Guinea, and Ghana. It has been used in varnishes. A medium-hard, pale yellow variety of copal resin obtained from trees of the genus Copaifera native to Sierra Leone, Guinea, and Ghana. It has been used in varnishes.</Note_Text>
